{"title":"沁园春  元旦·中美建交","authors":["金尧如"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":1,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沁园春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"元旦·中美建交"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金尧如"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华国文章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又增新页，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中美敦邦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望台湾海峡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一衣带水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太平洋上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里波光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日暖亚洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风流天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总赖东君有主张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾记否？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掷银球小小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转动玄黄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间正道沧桑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对风物长宜放眼量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想后之视今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹今视昔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今之视后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂可守常。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄语草山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤悬难久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万台胞尽北望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为宏图四化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿翱翔。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}